<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="guilty-adj">guilty <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡɪlti/    美 / 'ɡɪlti/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>内疚的；惭愧的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>I felt guilty about / at</strong> breaking my promise.
我对违背诺言感到内疚。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>犯罪的；有罪的</strong></h4>
<p>反 innocent </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be <strong>guilty of</strong> a crime
犯罪</p></div></div>